_sText:
An update to my Previous Aim_berlin_v3 a fun map where you play as either the east german (CT) or Nazi's (T)

If you are T you're going to be standing in a tower shooting every treespasser! but be aware!
If your CT you need to run your ass of to reach the other side of the wall, where you can Kill the T slowly and painfully.. it maybe seem unfair but it isnt if you play it regulary..

ps. thx for all the good comments i got! it made me see that the previous Aim_berlin_v3 Was  very crappy made :D

enjoy
